<tr id="L68"><td><a href="#L68">68</a></td><td>UHURA [on monitor]:  That's what bothers me, sir. Impossible to locate. There wasn't enough of it. Sensors show nothing in the area, but it was a strong signal, as though it was very close.</td></tr>

